'''Aodh Mac Dónaill''' (Anglicized: Hugh McDonnell) was a scribe from [[County Meath]]. Among the works he transcribed was ''Seachrán Charn tSiadhail'' by [[Tarlach Rua Mac Dónaill]]. It is now contained in a manuscript house in the Public Library, [[Belfast]].

